'''喬納森·查爾斯·葛雷'''（{{lang-en|Jonathan Charles Gray}}，{{bd|1991年|11月5日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於德州遊騎兵。他是[[2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]的選秀探花，先前曾效力過科羅拉多洛磯。
==職業生涯==
===科羅拉多洛磯===
2013年大聯盟選秀前，葛雷原本是狀元呼聲很高的人選。不過太空人後來選擇Brady Aiken作為狀元，而葛雷最終掉到第三順位被洛磯選走。葛雷在2015年8月4日登上大聯盟，他在這年拿下0勝2敗，防禦率5.53。<ref name=debut>{{cite web|url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28576630/jon-gray-scheduled-make-major-league-debut-rockies|title=Jon Gray scheduled to make major-league debut for Rockies against Mariners: Rockies fans have been waiting for Gray's debut all season|first=Patrick|last=Saunders|work=The Denver Post|date=August 2, 2015|access-date=August 3, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201545/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_28576630/jon-gray-scheduled-make-major-league-debut-rockies|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來他在休賽季加入曲球作為武器球種。<ref name=curveball>{{cite web|url=http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_29533488/jon-gray-adds-curveball-seeks-improvement-2nd-season-rockies|title=Jon Gray adds curveball, seeks improvement in 2nd season with Rockies: Colorado's top pick in 2013 makes tweaks, ready to make his mark|first=Patrick|last=Saunders|work=The Denver Post|date=February 18, 2016|access-date=February 25, 2016|archive-date=2016-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223001336/http://www.denverpost.com/rockies/ci_29533488/jon-gray-adds-curveball-seeks-improvement-2nd-season-rockies|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年球季初，葛雷因為腹部肌肉緊繃而進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/15058095/jon-gray-colorado-rockies-sidelined-couple-weeks-abdominal-strain |title=Jon Gray of Colorado Rockies sidelined couple weeks with abdominal strain |publisher=Espn.com |date=March 24, 2016 |access-date=September 26, 2017 |archive-date=2017-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926100622/http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/15058095/jon-gray-colorado-rockies-sidelined-couple-weeks-abdominal-strain |dead-url=no }}</ref>後來他在5月13日拿下大聯盟首勝，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2016/may/13/jon-gray-earns-1st-big-league-win-rockies-beat-met/|last=Graham|first=Pat|title=Jon Gray earns first major league win, Rockies beat Mets 5–2|publisher=The Washington Times|date=May 13, 2016|access-date=May 13, 2016|archive-date=2017-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170817080700/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2016/may/13/jon-gray-earns-1st-big-league-win-rockies-beat-met/|dead-url=no}}</ref>整年他拿下10勝10敗，防禦率4.61。<ref>{{cite web |last=Saunders |first=Patrick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/2017/06/29/slumping-rockies-counting-on-jon-gray/ |title=Slumping Rockies counting on return of Jon Gray, and return of offense, as second half begins – The Denver Post |publisher=Denverpost.com |access-date=September 26, 2017 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115001235/https://www.denverpost.com/2017/06/29/slumping-rockies-counting-on-jon-gray/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年，葛雷成為球隊的開幕戰先發。<ref name=openingday>{{cite web |last=Groke |first=Nick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/2017/03/30/jon-gray-rockies-opening-day-starter/ |title=Jon Gray named Rockies’ opening day starter for 2017. After that, questions remain. – The Denver Post |publisher=Denverpost.com |date=March 30, 2017 |access-date=September 26, 2017 |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414143455/https://www.denverpost.com/2017/03/30/jon-gray-rockies-opening-day-starter/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>4月份，他因為左腳出現疲勞性骨折而進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web |last=Harding |first=Thomas |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/224375750/jon-gray-on-disabled-list-with-foot-injury/ |title=Jon Gray on disabled list with foot injury | MLB.com |publisher=M.mlb.com |access-date=September 26, 2017 |archive-date=2017-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926142859/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/224375750/jon-gray-on-disabled-list-with-foot-injury/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>7月5日，他敲出了大聯盟首轟。<ref>{{cite web|title=Jon Gray launches first career home run at 467 feet|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/19845985/colorado-rockies-pitcher-jon-gray-launches-first-career-home-run-467-feet|publisher=ESPN|access-date=July 5, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109035629/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/19845985/colorado-rockies-pitcher-jon-gray-launches-first-career-home-run-467-feet|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在這年拿下10勝，防禦率3.67。

2018年球季，他的防禦率因為過高導致他在球季中被下放3A調整。<ref>{{cite web |title=Rockies send struggling Jon Gray to Triple-A |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/rockies-option-jon-gray-to-triple-a/c-283652912 |publisher=MLB |access-date=June 30, 2018 |archive-date=2018-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701002033/https://www.mlb.com/news/rockies-option-jon-gray-to-triple-a/c-283652912 |dead-url=no }}</ref>雖然後來成功回歸大聯盟，<ref>{{cite web |last=Saunders |first=Patrick |url=https://www.denverpost.com/2018/07/13/rockies-senzatela-hoffman/ |title=Jon Gray set to be recalled from Triple-A and will start Saturday; Antonio Senzatela, who was scheduled to start tonight, headed to DL – The Denver Post |publisher=Denverpost.com |date=July 13, 2018 |access-date=January 9, 2019 |archive-date=2019-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212153909/https://www.denverpost.com/2018/07/13/rockies-senzatela-hoffman/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過球隊看在他例行賽高達5.12的防禦率，加上被敲出27轟，因此未將他放入國聯分區賽的25人名單內。<ref>{{cite web |last=Saunders |first=Patrick |url=https://www.denverpost.com/2018/11/13/rockies-jon-gray-strength-confidence-2019/ |title=Rockies' Jon Gray, working to build strength, plans to rebound in 2019 |publisher=Denverpost.com |date=November 13, 2018 |access-date=January 9, 2019 |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414112735/https://www.denverpost.com/2018/11/13/rockies-jon-gray-strength-confidence-2019/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2019年，葛雷投出11勝8敗，不過他又因為傷勢缺席後段賽季。2020年，葛雷整年僅先發8場比賽，然後再度受傷進入傷兵名單中。這年他的各項投球數據都是生涯新低。
==個人生活==
葛雷的爺爺是一位切羅基人(美國東南方的一個原住民族群)，<ref>{{cite web |last=Harding |first=Thomas |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/197631590/rockies-jon-gray-proud-of-cherokee-roots/ |title=Rockies' Jon Gray proud of Cherokee roots | MLB.com |publisher=M.mlb.com |access-date=September 26, 2017 |archive-date=2017-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926143040/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/197631590/rockies-jon-gray-proud-of-cherokee-roots/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而葛雷本身已婚。<ref>{{cite web |last=Groke |first=Nick |url=http://www.denverpost.com/2017/04/11/jon-gray-cuts-hair-colorado-rockies/ |title=Rockies ace Jon Gray loses "alter ego," but shears off hair for Locks of Love |publisher=Denverpost.com |access-date=September 26, 2017 |archive-date=2018-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311013536/https://www.denverpost.com/2017/04/11/jon-gray-cuts-hair-colorado-rockies/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他的哥哥傑克曾在東北州立大學擔任美式足球後衛。<ref name=espn>{{cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/college-sports/story/_/id/9184897/oklahoma-jonathan-gray-climbed-mlb-draft-boards-spring-college-baseball |title=Oklahoma's Jonathan Gray has climbed MLB draft boards this spring – college baseball – ESPN |publisher=Espn.go.com |date=January 1, 2008 |access-date=April 19, 2013 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304133106/http://espn.go.com/college-sports/story/_/id/9184897/oklahoma-jonathan-gray-climbed-mlb-draft-boards-spring-college-baseball |dead-url=no }}</ref>
